# ADI MSRP Scraper

Purpose: scrape brand camera MSRP from ADI (auth required), export to Excel, and produce delta reports.

## Quick start
1) Python 3.12+ installed
2) In this folder:
   - \.venv\ virtual env
   - \.env\ (copy from \.env.example\)

### Setup
\\\powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
playwright install chromium
\\\

### Run
\\\powershell
python src\main.py --brand Hanwha --headless
\\\

### One-click
Double-click \efresh_hanwha.bat\.

